name: my_view
view_definition: SELECT agg_ex.my_sum(my_table.i) AS my_sum,\n    agg_ex.my_avg(my_table.i) AS my_avg\n   FROM agg_ex.my_table;

name: basic_view
view_definition:
SELECT ordinary_table.basic_,
    ordinary_table._basic,
    ordinary_table.nested,
    ordinary_table._nested
   FROM composite_type_examples.ordinary_table;

name: dependent_view
view_definition: SELECT each.key,\n    each.value\n   FROM extension_example.each('""=>"1", "b"=>NULL, "aaa"=>"bq"'::extension_example.hstore) each(key, value);

name: bv1
view_definition:
SELECT b1.a,
    b1.b
   FROM regress_rls_schema.b1
  WHERE b1.a > 0;

name: rls_sbv
view_definition:
SELECT y1.a,
    y1.b
   FROM regress_rls_schema.y1
  WHERE regress_rls_schema.f_leak(y1.b);

name: v2
view_definition:

    s2.y
   FROM regress_rls_schema.s2
